SO ARE THEY GONNA
GO TO JAIL FOR IT OR WHAT?

00:11.311 --> 00:12.813
PERHAPS.
WE'RE BUILDING A CASE.

00:12.813 --> 00:13.947
THEY'RE NOT
GOOD PEOPLE, MAN.

00:13.947 --> 00:15.381
I WANT HIM DEAD.

