02:45.111 --> 02:47.881
YOU OKAY?

02:47.881 --> 02:48.882
YEAH.

02:48.882 --> 02:50.884
YOU SURE?

02:50.884 --> 02:52.452
YEAH.

02:52.452 --> 02:54.721
OKAY.

02:54.721 --> 02:57.357
GOOD.

02:57.357 --> 02:58.992
THANK YOU.

02:58.992 --> 03:01.134
YEAH.

03:01.134 --> 03:03.870
HE NEEDED TO GO.

03:03.870 --> 03:06.907
I KNOW.

03:06.907 --> 03:09.342
BUT IT'S ALL GOOD NOW.

03:12.178 --> 03:15.215
I KNOW YOU NEVER WANTED TO BE
IN YOUR FAMILY'S BUSINESS.

03:17.951 --> 03:21.421
GUESS I'M IN IT NOW.

03:21.421 --> 03:23.289
IS IT SO BAD?

03:23.289 --> 03:25.759
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

03:25.759 --> 03:27.528
[ SIGHS ] I MEAN...

03:27.528 --> 03:29.830
THEY TAKE CARE
OF THINGS LIKE HIM,

03:29.830 --> 03:34.601
LIKE THEY TOOK CARE
OF THIS.

03:34.601 --> 03:38.304
YEAH, BUT IT GOES A LOT
DEEPER THAN THAT.

03:38.304 --> 03:40.006
YEAH, WELL, THAT SON OF A BITCH
KILLED MY SON,

03:40.006 --> 03:41.374
SO I DON'T CARE.

03:41.374 --> 03:45.546
YEAH. WELL, YOU SAVED
A LOT OF PEOPLE'S KIDS TONIGHT.

03:45.546 --> 03:48.749
I KNOW.

03:48.749 --> 03:51.217
DO YOU?

03:51.217 --> 03:53.920
YEAH, HE WAS SELLING
THAT STUFF.

03:53.920 --> 03:55.556
HE JUST DIDN'T CARE.
NO.

03:55.556 --> 03:58.358
NO, THAT'S NOT
WHAT I MEAN.

03:58.358 --> 03:59.560
WHAT?

04:02.202 --> 04:04.605
MY GRANDMOTHER...

04:04.605 --> 04:06.306
WHEN HE SHOT AT ME,

04:06.306 --> 04:08.341
AND SHE FOUND OUT, IT ‐‐

04:08.341 --> 04:10.511
IT OPENED
A LOT OF OLD WOUNDS.

04:12.345 --> 04:14.380
MM.

04:14.380 --> 04:16.016
BLOODY THURSDAY.

04:16.016 --> 04:18.552
YOU KNOW ABOUT THAT?

04:18.552 --> 04:19.753
I WAS A KID.

04:19.753 --> 04:22.022
YEAH.

04:22.022 --> 04:24.257
YEAH, ME TOO.

04:24.257 --> 04:26.527
PROJECTS WERE BLOODY
THAT DAY.

04:26.527 --> 04:28.261
YEAH, WELL...

04:28.261 --> 04:29.362
I MEAN, THAT'S KIND OF
WHAT I'M SAYING.

04:29.362 --> 04:31.431
THAT'S...

04:31.431 --> 04:32.866
THAT'S HOW YOU SAVED
A LOT OF LIVES

04:32.866 --> 04:36.936
'CAUSE MY GRANDMA,
SHE WAS ‐‐

04:36.936 --> 04:42.576
SHE WAS ABOUT TO RAIN DOWN HELL
ON THE HOOD.

04:42.576 --> 04:46.412
WELL...
WE DID THE WORLD A FAVOR.

04:46.412 --> 04:47.948
YOU DELIVERED HIM.

04:49.783 --> 04:51.117
HMM.

04:51.117 --> 04:52.485
I'LL TAKE IT.

04:54.721 --> 04:57.423
SHE'S GONNA WANT
TO THANK YOU.

04:57.423 --> 04:59.025
SHE JUST DID.

04:59.025 --> 05:00.460
MORE.

05:00.460 --> 05:03.303
YOU KNOW, IN PERSON.

05:03.303 --> 05:05.506
I DON'T THINK SO.

05:09.843 --> 05:13.379
I DON'T THINK
YOU WANT TO INSULT HER.

05:13.379 --> 05:15.281
SO...

05:15.281 --> 05:18.284
MNM. I REALLY
DON'T THINK SO.

05:18.284 --> 05:20.954
ALL RIGHT.

05:20.954 --> 05:23.323
I'LL TRY TO GET
AROUND IT, BUT...

05:23.323 --> 05:25.358
YOU KNOW,
THEY GOT RULES.

05:25.358 --> 05:27.493
IT'S CRAZY.

05:27.493 --> 05:30.430
I KNOW.

05:30.430 --> 05:32.999
I MEAN, HOW DO YOU
KNOW HER ANYWAY?

05:32.999 --> 05:35.536
I MEAN, I NEVER KNEW
YOU HAD BEEN TO THE RESTAURANT.

05:37.904 --> 05:39.172
SHE KIDNAPPED ME.

05:39.172 --> 05:41.141
WHAT?

05:41.141 --> 05:42.876
[ SCOFFS ]

05:42.876 --> 05:45.245
FOR JIM CRYER.

05:45.245 --> 05:49.015
SHE THREATENED ME
TO LEAVE HIM ALONE.

05:49.015 --> 05:50.150
I DIDN'T KNOW WHERE I WAS

05:50.150 --> 05:52.953
UNTIL I WAS
SITTING IN THAT RESTAURANT.

05:54.254 --> 05:55.989
AND THEN...

05:55.989 --> 05:57.057
I REMEMBER
IN THE BASEMENT

05:57.057 --> 05:58.992
HEARING ALL THOSE
PEOPLE UPSTAIRS

05:58.992 --> 06:03.737
LAUGHING
AND HAVING A GOOD TIME.

06:03.737 --> 06:06.907
YEAH, THAT'S WHERE
THEY TAKE PEOPLE.

06:06.907 --> 06:08.374
I KNOW.

06:08.374 --> 06:11.745
BUT, USUALLY,
THEY NEVER LEAVE.

06:11.745 --> 06:13.614
WELL, I DID.

06:16.416 --> 06:18.519
[ Sighing ] YEAH.
YOU'RE LUCKY.

06:20.721 --> 06:22.455
I'M SURPRISED YOU NEVER
TOLD ME ABOUT THAT.

06:22.455 --> 06:24.090
[ SCOFFS ]

06:24.090 --> 06:27.160
HOW WOULD I HAVE
TOLD YOU?

06:27.160 --> 06:29.462
BY THE TIME
I GOT NEAR A PHONE,

06:29.462 --> 06:32.733
I HAD LOST EVERYTHING.

06:32.733 --> 06:38.204
THEY NEARLY BLEW MY EARDRUM
OUT WITH A SHOTGUN.

06:38.204 --> 06:42.175
SO THERE'S NO NEED TO...

06:42.175 --> 06:44.711
GIVE A FORMAL THANK YOU.

06:44.711 --> 06:46.379
WELL, SHE OWES YOU.

06:46.379 --> 06:47.380
YOU NEVER KNOW.

06:47.380 --> 06:49.382
ONE DAY,
IT MIGHT COME IN HANDY.

06:52.853 --> 06:54.187
[ SCOFFS ]

07:01.101 --> 07:03.436
MITCH, CAN YOU
JUST TAKE ME SOMEWHERE?

07:03.436 --> 07:05.005
YEAH.

07:05.005 --> 07:06.039
THANKS.

07:06.039 --> 07:07.741
ALL RIGHT.

07:07.741 --> 07:09.342
[ ENGINE STARTS ]

07:09.342 --> 07:14.515
♪♪♪♪

07:14.515 --> 07:16.182
[ TRANSMISSION SHIFTS ]

07:16.182 --> 07:17.551
[ ENGINES STOPS ]

07:19.686 --> 07:21.221
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

07:23.824 --> 07:27.493
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]
FEEL LIKE DRIVING, BABY?

07:27.493 --> 07:29.195
YEAH. SURE.

07:36.703 --> 07:39.573
♪♪♪♪

08:00.193 --> 08:01.234
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

08:01.234 --> 08:03.169
[ SIGHS ]

08:09.075 --> 08:11.878
IT'S ALL RIGHT, MOM.
IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.

08:14.615 --> 08:18.418
YOUR SISTER CALLED ME.

08:18.418 --> 08:19.820
WHAT'D SHE SAY?

08:23.624 --> 08:26.693
SHE WANTED TO KNOW
WHY I DIDN'T PROTECT HIM.

08:26.693 --> 08:28.394
MOMMA...

08:28.394 --> 08:30.430
YEP.

08:30.430 --> 08:32.933
THAT'S WHAT SHE SAID.

08:32.933 --> 08:34.200
LOOK, YOU KNOW CANDACE.

08:34.200 --> 08:35.368
SHE'S...

08:38.872 --> 08:41.241
SHE WANTED TO KNOW WHY...

08:41.241 --> 08:43.176
THAT BABY GOT SHOT,
AND I DIDN'T.

08:43.176 --> 08:45.011
WHAT?

08:45.011 --> 08:46.012
SHE SAID THAT TO YOU?

08:46.012 --> 08:47.413
YEAH.

08:50.116 --> 08:52.318
LOOK, YOU CAN'T TAKE...

08:52.318 --> 08:53.787
SHE'S JUST UPSET, OKAY.

08:53.787 --> 08:56.422
THAT'S ALL.
SHE'S JUST UPSET.

08:56.422 --> 08:58.024
WHY DID HE GET SHOT
AND NOT ME?

08:58.024 --> 09:00.901
LOOK, YOU CAN'T SAY THAT.
DON'T SAY THAT.

09:02.836 --> 09:04.738
I WAS C‐‐ COVERING HIM.

09:04.738 --> 09:06.740
I KNOW.

09:06.740 --> 09:08.208
I WAS COVERING HIM...

09:08.208 --> 09:09.576
I KNOW.

09:11.745 --> 09:13.647
...AND IT DIDN'T
TOUCH ME. WHY?

09:17.383 --> 09:18.552
I DON'T KNOW.

09:22.923 --> 09:24.991
SHE BLAMES ME.

09:24.991 --> 09:26.092
LOOK, MOMMY.

09:26.092 --> 09:27.628
LOOK...

09:27.628 --> 09:30.130
THIS IS NOT YOUR FAULT.

09:30.130 --> 09:31.297
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

09:31.297 --> 09:32.465
[ Voice breaking ]
I TRIED, BENNY.

09:32.465 --> 09:35.769
I KNOW.

09:35.769 --> 09:37.571
I TRIED.
I KNOW YOU DID, MOM.

09:37.571 --> 09:38.905
I KNOW YOU DID.

09:41.274 --> 09:43.777
[ SIGHS ] THAT GIRL.

09:43.777 --> 09:47.247
♪♪♪♪

09:47.247 --> 09:48.682
SHH.

09:50.984 --> 09:53.019
[ SIGHS ]

09:53.019 --> 09:54.487
I'M ALL OUT.

09:57.423 --> 09:59.459
I'M OUT OF PATIENCE.

09:59.459 --> 10:02.669
I'M OUT OF...

10:02.669 --> 10:03.637
PRAYER.

10:03.637 --> 10:05.405
I'M OUT OF FAITH.

10:07.007 --> 10:10.476
I'M JUST EMPTY.

10:10.476 --> 10:15.015
I MEAN, WHAT'S THE POINT
OF DOING THE RIGHT THING?

10:15.015 --> 10:16.482
LET'S GO TO CHURCH.

10:16.482 --> 10:19.185
HMM?

10:19.185 --> 10:20.821
I DON'T WANT TO GO
TO CHURCH.

10:20.821 --> 10:21.888
COME ON.

10:21.888 --> 10:22.956
YOU'LL FEEL BETTER.

10:22.956 --> 10:26.492
[ Sternly ] I DON'T WANT
TO GO TO CHURCH.

10:26.492 --> 10:28.929
LOOK, IT'S JUST LIKE
YOU ALWAYS TOLD ME.

10:28.929 --> 10:32.265
WHAT'D YOU ALWAYS
TELL ME?

10:32.265 --> 10:34.768
NO MATTER
HOW BAD THINGS GET,

10:34.768 --> 10:38.004
GOD WILL ALWAYS MAKE A WAY,
AND THIS IS NO DIFFERENT.

10:38.004 --> 10:40.306
BENNY, I DON'T IF MY GOD'S
GONNA MAKE A WAY OUT OF THIS.

10:42.308 --> 10:45.411
THAT BABY IS GONE.

10:47.648 --> 10:48.915
SO, YOU'RE SAYING
YOU DON'T TRUST HIM?

10:48.915 --> 10:52.118
I'M SAYING I'M TIRED.

10:52.118 --> 10:53.720
I'M SAYING THIS LIFE
AIN'T BEEN NOTHING

10:53.720 --> 10:57.057
BUT FROM STRUGGLE TO STRUGGLE,
AND I'M TIRED.

11:01.167 --> 11:03.103
LET'S PRAY. COME ON.

11:03.103 --> 11:04.605
YOU PRAY.

11:06.507 --> 11:07.541
I NEED YOU TO SHOW ME.

11:07.541 --> 11:10.577
NO, I ALREADY
SHOWED YOU, BABY.

11:10.577 --> 11:12.112
ALL RIGHT.

11:12.112 --> 11:13.547
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

11:13.547 --> 11:15.782
ALL RIGHT.
LOOK, LET'S PRAY, UH...

11:15.782 --> 11:17.217
[ SIGHS ]

11:19.119 --> 11:20.486
LET'S PRAY THE PRAYER
THAT YOU TAUGHT ME.

11:20.486 --> 11:21.655
HUH.

11:25.458 --> 11:28.629
I'M ALL OUT.

11:28.629 --> 11:30.163
I'M OUT.

11:32.365 --> 11:34.234
LET'S GO.

11:34.234 --> 11:36.336
WHERE WE GOING?
I DON'T KNOW.

11:38.639 --> 11:40.206
I REALLY DON'T KNOW.

11:42.743 --> 11:45.512
OUR FATHER...

11:45.512 --> 11:47.180
WHICH ART IN HEAVEN...

11:49.783 --> 11:53.319
...HALLOWED BE THY...

11:53.319 --> 11:55.355
HALLOWED BE THY NAME.

11:59.459 --> 12:02.869
THY KINGDOM COME...

12:02.869 --> 12:04.738
THY WILL BE DONE...

12:07.307 --> 12:08.942
COME ON. HELP ME.

12:13.647 --> 12:15.649
AS IT IS ON EARTH...

12:19.285 --> 12:20.854
[ SIGHS ]

12:20.854 --> 12:22.523
...AS IT IS IN HEAVEN.

12:28.261 --> 12:30.030
GIVE US THIS DAY...

12:30.030 --> 12:32.232
MAMA, HELP ME.

12:32.232 --> 12:36.503
...OUR DAILY BREAD ‐‐
HELP ‐‐

12:36.503 --> 12:39.606
FORGIVE US OUR DEBTS...

12:39.606 --> 12:42.543
AS WE FORGIVE OUR DEBTORS.

12:42.543 --> 12:46.379
AND LEAD US NOT
INTO TEMPTATION...

12:48.314 --> 12:51.317
...BUT DELIVER US
FROM EVIL...

12:51.317 --> 12:54.555
♪♪♪♪

12:54.555 --> 12:57.624
FOR THINE
IS THE KINGDOM...

12:57.624 --> 12:59.760
POWER, AND GLORY...

12:59.760 --> 13:02.636
FOREVER...

13:02.636 --> 13:04.370
AND EVER.

13:04.370 --> 13:06.239
MAMA, HELP.

13:06.239 --> 13:07.508
[ Voice breaking ]
MAMA, HELP ME.

13:12.813 --> 13:15.348
AMEN.

13:26.059 --> 13:28.428
[ ENGINE STARTS ]

13:32.298 --> 13:36.069
♪♪♪♪

13:49.382 --> 13:51.084
[ KNOCKS ON DOOR ]

13:56.122 --> 13:57.223
WHO IS IT?

13:57.223 --> 14:00.527
IT'S DAVID.

14:00.527 --> 14:02.736
YOU SOUNDED UPSET
WHEN YOU CALLED ME.

14:02.736 --> 14:04.070
YEAH.

14:04.070 --> 14:05.171
IS IT MY WIFE?

14:05.171 --> 14:07.007
NO. NO. IT'S...

14:07.007 --> 14:08.509
WHAT IS IT?

14:08.509 --> 14:10.376
NOTHING. I'M OKAY.

14:10.376 --> 14:11.477
ERICA, WHAT'S WRONG?

14:11.477 --> 14:13.814
I'M OKAY.
YOU'RE SHAKING.

14:13.814 --> 14:15.882
NO. I'M OKAY.

14:15.882 --> 14:18.819
WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR FACE?

14:18.819 --> 14:19.853
IT'S OKAY.
NO. IT'S NOT.

14:19.853 --> 14:22.455
LOOK AT ME.

14:22.455 --> 14:23.557
WHO DID THIS TO YOU?

14:23.557 --> 14:24.591
NO ONE.

14:24.591 --> 14:25.826
WAS IT VERONICA?
NO. NO.

14:25.826 --> 14:28.895
ARE YOU SURE?
YES. NO.

14:28.895 --> 14:30.597
WHAT HAPPENED?

14:30.597 --> 14:31.598
I...

14:31.598 --> 14:34.434
DO YOU KNOW
WHO DID THIS TO YOU?

14:34.434 --> 14:35.335
I JUST...

14:35.335 --> 14:36.937
DAMN IT. DAVID, WAIT.

14:36.937 --> 14:38.805
WAIT. WAIT!
I'LL BE BACK.

14:38.805 --> 14:39.806
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

14:39.806 --> 14:41.374
I'M GOING TO TALK
TO VERONICA.

14:41.374 --> 14:42.776
NO!

14:42.776 --> 14:43.877
NO. IT'S NOT HER.

14:43.877 --> 14:45.211
ARE YOU SURE?
YES. I ‐‐

14:45.211 --> 14:48.114
YES, IT'S NOT HER.

14:48.114 --> 14:49.550
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

14:54.354 --> 14:57.958
DAVID, I HAVE ‐‐
I HAVE A PROBLEM.

14:57.958 --> 15:01.301
WHAT KIND OF A PROBLEM?

15:01.301 --> 15:02.402
I ‐‐

15:02.402 --> 15:04.270
I DON'T KNOW.

15:04.270 --> 15:07.073
[ SIGHS ]
JUST TELL ME.

15:07.073 --> 15:08.241
I JUST MET YOU,

15:08.241 --> 15:09.810
AND I DON'T WANT
TO PUT THIS BURDEN ON YOU.

15:09.810 --> 15:12.312
ERICA. ERICA.

15:12.312 --> 15:16.783
TELL ME WHAT IT IS.

15:16.783 --> 15:18.852
I DON'T KNOW HOW.

15:18.852 --> 15:20.286
JUST SAY IT.

15:24.457 --> 15:25.491
I DIDN'T ‐‐

15:25.491 --> 15:27.728
I DIDN'T TELL YOU
EVERYTHING ABOUT ME.

15:29.195 --> 15:31.565
OKAY.

15:31.565 --> 15:34.635
EVERYTHING IS NOT GOOD.

15:34.635 --> 15:36.202
ALL RIGHT.

15:36.202 --> 15:37.538
I'M LISTENING.

15:37.538 --> 15:39.973
PLEASE DON'T BE UPSET.
I WON'T BE.

15:39.973 --> 15:41.107
JUST TELL ME

15:41.107 --> 15:44.444
WHAT IS GOING ON
WITH YOU.

15:44.444 --> 15:48.081
I'M RUNNING FROM SOMEONE.

15:48.081 --> 15:51.284
IS IT THE POLICE?
NO.

15:51.284 --> 15:53.554
IS IT AN ILLEGAL MATTER?

15:57.190 --> 15:59.793
IT'S MY FIANCé.

15:59.793 --> 16:03.670
FIANCé?

16:03.670 --> 16:06.172
YEAH, HE WANTS ME
TO MARRY HIM

16:06.172 --> 16:07.674
AND I DON'T WANT TO.

16:07.674 --> 16:09.543
OKAY. OKAY.

16:09.543 --> 16:13.046
HE'S LIKE YOUR WIFE,
EXCEPT HE BEATS ME AND...

16:13.046 --> 16:14.581
DAMN.
I JUST ‐‐

16:14.581 --> 16:16.349
[ STAMMERS ]
I NEED TO GET AWAY.

16:16.349 --> 16:18.218
OKAY.
I JUST WANT TO GO AWAY.

16:18.218 --> 16:19.786
OKAY. OKAY.

16:19.786 --> 16:22.823
DID HE DO THIS TO YOU?

16:22.823 --> 16:25.191
YES.
WHAT'S HIS NAME?

16:25.191 --> 16:26.192
[ MUTTERS ]

16:26.192 --> 16:29.930
[ Sternly ]
ERICA, WHAT IS HIS NAME?

16:29.930 --> 16:31.832
I'M NOT GONNA TELL YOU.

16:36.102 --> 16:37.671
I CAN HELP YOU.

16:37.671 --> 16:39.305
I DON'T ‐‐

16:39.305 --> 16:41.542
I DON'T WANT HELP.

16:41.542 --> 16:43.744
I JUST WANT TO GO AWAY
THAT'S ALL.

16:43.744 --> 16:45.445
OKAY.

16:45.445 --> 16:46.479
I JUST NEED TO GET AWAY
FROM HERE.

16:46.479 --> 16:49.115
OKAY. I CAN DO THAT.

16:49.115 --> 16:51.652
[ SNIFFLES ]

16:51.652 --> 16:52.753
I JUST NEED MONEY.

16:52.753 --> 16:56.156
OKAY. WHAT DO YOU NEED?

16:56.156 --> 16:58.124
I DON'T KNOW WHAT I NEED.

16:58.124 --> 16:59.993
JUST HELP ME.
OKAY.

16:59.993 --> 17:03.269
ERICA, I CAN REALLY HELP YOU
IF YOU TELL ME HIS NAME.

17:03.269 --> 17:07.007
[ GASPS ]
WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DO?

17:07.007 --> 17:09.175
I USE TO BE A JUDGE,
AND I'M A LAWYER.

17:09.175 --> 17:12.713
I CAN HAVE HIM ARRESTED.
I ‐‐ I CAN TAKE CARE OF THIS.

17:15.348 --> 17:17.317
NO, JUST GET ME AWAY
FROM HERE PLEASE.

17:17.317 --> 17:19.319
OKAY. OKAY.
DOES HE KNOW YOU'RE HERE?

17:19.319 --> 17:20.954
YES.
OKAY.

17:20.954 --> 17:22.623
GET YOUR THINGS TOGETHER.

17:22.623 --> 17:23.690
LET'S GO.
[ SNIFFLES ]

17:23.690 --> 17:26.026
THANK YOU.

17:26.026 --> 17:28.094
I'MA GET YOU
SOME PLACE SAFE.

17:28.094 --> 17:31.898
CAN WE ‐‐ CAN WE GO OUT
THE BACK STAIRCASE, PLEASE?

17:31.898 --> 17:35.368
♪♪♪♪

17:38.104 --> 17:39.806
IT'S OKAY.

17:39.806 --> 17:41.207
I'M GONNA
PROTECT YOU NOW.

17:41.207 --> 17:42.342
THANK YOU.
OKAY.

17:42.342 --> 17:43.744
YOU DON'T EVER HAVE
TO WORRY ABOUT SOMEBODY

17:43.744 --> 17:46.780
DOING THIS TO YOU AGAIN.

17:46.780 --> 17:48.481
THANK YOU.

17:48.481 --> 17:50.150
I'M SORRY.

17:50.150 --> 17:51.818
I'M SO SORRY
I DIDN'T TELL YOU.

17:51.818 --> 17:52.953
IT'S FINE.

17:52.953 --> 17:55.321
IT'S JUST ‐‐
I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT TO SAY.

17:59.092 --> 18:01.367
IT'S OKAY.

18:13.213 --> 18:14.515
Veronica: [ Distantly ]
YOU'RE WHERE?

18:14.515 --> 18:17.718
OKAY, MAKE SURE
YOU IRON THOSE SHEETS, OKAY.

18:24.457 --> 18:25.759
HELLO.

18:25.759 --> 18:28.428
HI.

18:28.428 --> 18:32.432
MELISSA, AREN'T YOU
GONNA SAY HI?

18:32.432 --> 18:34.200
HI.

18:34.200 --> 18:37.604
WELL, YOU GAVE US
QUITE A SCARE.

18:37.604 --> 18:39.305
ALL OF US.

18:39.305 --> 18:41.608
DON'T EVER DO THAT
AGAIN, OKAY.

18:41.608 --> 18:42.809
SHE WON'T.

18:42.809 --> 18:44.678
I HOPE NOT.

18:44.678 --> 18:46.647
SHE WAS UPSET
ABOUT HER FATHER.

18:46.647 --> 18:49.750
OH, I CAN
UNDERSTAND THAT.

18:49.750 --> 18:53.086
BUT SUICIDE IS
NEVER THE ANSWER.

18:53.086 --> 18:54.621
SHE GETS IT.

18:54.621 --> 18:56.790
IT'S NOT.
SHE KNOWS THAT NOW.

18:56.790 --> 18:58.725
I HOPE SO...

18:58.725 --> 18:59.926
SHE DOES.

18:59.926 --> 19:02.869
...BECAUSE WE'VE GONE
TO GREAT PAINS TO BE SURE THAT

19:02.869 --> 19:05.138
WE HAVE A NICE PLACE
FOR YOU AND FOR THE BABY.

19:05.138 --> 19:07.307
SHE GETS IT.
SHE GETS IT.

19:07.307 --> 19:09.009
SHE DOES.

19:09.009 --> 19:10.310
DOES SHE REALLY?

19:10.310 --> 19:11.545
YES.

19:14.681 --> 19:18.652
SO HOW ARE THINGS COMING
FOR THE FUNERAL?

19:18.652 --> 19:20.754
WELL...

19:20.754 --> 19:21.988
OKAY.

19:26.760 --> 19:30.496
AND THIS IS WHERE
YOU WOULD LIKE FOR ME TO SAY...

19:30.496 --> 19:32.065
WHAT?

19:32.065 --> 19:33.634
OH.

19:33.634 --> 19:34.735
NOTHING.

19:38.505 --> 19:39.806
WHAT IS IT?

19:42.609 --> 19:44.845
WELL, THE INSURANCE WON'T
COVER IT ALL AND I...

19:44.845 --> 19:46.847
AND YOU NEED
ANOTHER LOAN?

19:46.847 --> 19:50.083
NO. NO.

19:50.083 --> 19:54.220
WELL,
UNTIL I SELL THE HOUSE.

19:54.220 --> 19:56.189
YOU'RE SELLING THE HOUSE?

19:56.189 --> 19:57.423
YES.

19:57.423 --> 20:00.393
SO I CAN PAY YOU
THE MORTGAGE.

20:00.393 --> 20:02.068
WHERE WILL YOU LIVE?

20:02.068 --> 20:05.238
MY SISTER IS IN DELAWARE.
SHE HAS ROOM FOR ME.

20:05.238 --> 20:09.175
♪♪♪♪

20:09.175 --> 20:11.444
I SEE.

20:11.444 --> 20:14.414
HOW MUCH DO YOU NEED?

20:14.414 --> 20:17.551
THEY'RE PUTTING TOGETHER
THE TOTAL NOW.

20:17.551 --> 20:19.485
CAN I GET BACK TO YOU?

20:19.485 --> 20:21.522
OF COURSE.

20:21.522 --> 20:24.157
YOU ALWAYS DO.

20:24.157 --> 20:27.060
YES. I DO.

20:27.060 --> 20:30.496
ALL RIGHT.

20:30.496 --> 20:32.265
AND SOMETHING SMELLS GOOD.

20:32.265 --> 20:33.534
YES.

20:33.534 --> 20:35.068
THAT WOULD BE DINNER.

20:35.068 --> 20:37.370
OH, OKAY.

20:44.444 --> 20:46.913
GOOD NIGHT.

20:46.913 --> 20:49.616
OH.

20:49.616 --> 20:51.017
OKAY.

20:52.719 --> 20:54.521
MELISSA.

20:54.521 --> 20:56.823
YES?

20:56.823 --> 20:59.693
I LOVE YOU, HONEY.

20:59.693 --> 21:02.736
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

21:02.736 --> 21:04.170
I'LL CALL YOU.

21:04.170 --> 21:05.539
YEAH.

21:08.975 --> 21:10.043
BYE, MRS. HARRINGTON.

21:10.043 --> 21:11.144
BYE‐BYE.

21:17.651 --> 21:20.153
[ DOOR OPENS ]

21:20.153 --> 21:22.723
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

21:22.723 --> 21:25.992
THAT BITCH WOULD
GET ON A GNATS NERVES.

21:25.992 --> 21:28.361
I DON'T KNOW
HOW YOU DO IT.

21:28.361 --> 21:30.564
IS SHE ON CRACK?

21:30.564 --> 21:32.599
NO.

21:32.599 --> 21:34.434
OH, WELL, SHE ACTS LIKE
SHE'S ON CRACK.

21:34.434 --> 21:37.003
LIKE, SHE ALWAYS
ASKING FOR MONEY.

21:37.003 --> 21:38.404
CAN I GET A FIVE?

21:38.404 --> 21:40.440
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:40.440 --> 21:42.776
SHE'S DISABLED.

21:42.776 --> 21:44.845
HMM?

21:44.845 --> 21:47.413
THAT BITCH
IS NOT DISABLED.

21:47.413 --> 21:49.315
SHE NEEDS TO DISABLE
THE REFRIGERATOR,

21:49.315 --> 21:52.318
IS WHAT SHE NEEDS TO DO.
YOU KNOW WHAT, MELISSA?

21:52.318 --> 21:53.920
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE
TO WATCH IT, BABY.

21:53.920 --> 21:55.321
BECAUSE IF
YOU DON'T WATCH IT,

21:55.321 --> 21:58.324
YOU'RE GONNA END UP
WITH SADDLEBAGS JUST LIKE HER.

21:58.324 --> 22:00.293
I TRY TO TELL
ALL THE LITTLE BLACK,

22:00.293 --> 22:01.467
GHETTO GIRLS THAT I KNOW.

22:01.467 --> 22:03.469
WELL, I ONLY KNOW,
LIKE, ONE OR TWO.

22:03.469 --> 22:05.171
BUT I TRY TO TELL THEM,
YOU KNOW,

22:05.171 --> 22:08.675
YOU CAN'T EAT SO MANY CARBS
AND PROCESSED FOOD.

22:08.675 --> 22:11.845
THEY AREN'T GOOD
FOR YOU.

22:11.845 --> 22:14.548
NOW, COME ON.
LET'S GET YOU UPSTAIRS.

22:14.548 --> 22:16.282
GET YOU SOME REST. OKAY.

22:16.282 --> 22:17.751
I'M FINE HERE.

22:17.751 --> 22:19.953
NO.

22:19.953 --> 22:21.622
YOU CAN'T STAY DOWN HERE.

22:21.622 --> 22:23.657
YOUR PLACE IS UPSTAIRS.

22:23.657 --> 22:25.225
COME ON.

22:48.081 --> 22:51.417
♪♪♪♪

22:51.417 --> 22:54.420
YOU LOOK SHOOK, DEAR.

22:54.420 --> 22:58.124
SEE, THIS WHAT HAPPENS WHEN
YOU LEAVE A MESS IN MY HOUSE.

23:00.026 --> 23:02.168
WHAT'D YOU THINK?

23:02.168 --> 23:06.006
DID YOU THINK I WAS GONNA GET
THE MAID TO CLEAN IT UP?

23:06.006 --> 23:08.174
SHE TALKS TOO MUCH,

23:08.174 --> 23:11.077
AND I CERTAINLY WASN'T
GONNA CLEAN IT UP.

23:12.412 --> 23:15.982
SO THAT LEAVES YOU.

23:15.982 --> 23:18.752
NOW I WANT YOU
TO CLEAN IT UP, OKAY.

23:18.752 --> 23:21.788
EVERY, EVERY OUNCE OF IT,

23:21.788 --> 23:24.725
THE MATTRESS
AND EVERYTHING.

23:24.725 --> 23:27.928
WHEN YOU'RE DONE,

23:27.928 --> 23:31.131
I DON'T WANT TO SEE
A SPEC OF RED ANYWHERE, OKAY?

23:32.599 --> 23:35.201
YES.

23:35.201 --> 23:37.437
I'M GONNA HAVE TO GO.

23:37.437 --> 23:40.273
I HAVE TO FIND MY CHECKBOOK

23:40.273 --> 23:42.943
BECAUSE YOUR RATCHET‐ASS MAMA
GONNA BE BACK HERE,

23:42.943 --> 23:44.645
WANTING SOME MONEY.

23:48.248 --> 23:51.785
I SURE HOPE
YOU'RE WORTH IT.

23:51.785 --> 23:56.156
THIS BABY BETTER
BE HEALTHY,

23:56.156 --> 23:57.624
AND IT BETTER BE CUTE.

24:02.402 --> 24:03.970
ENJOY CLEANING.

24:10.010 --> 24:13.580
♪♪♪♪

24:42.475 --> 24:45.846
HI.

24:45.846 --> 24:49.049
HI.

24:49.049 --> 24:51.652
I WAS WAITING
FOR YOU TO GET BACK.

24:51.652 --> 24:52.753
YEAH?

24:52.753 --> 24:54.721
YEAH.

24:54.721 --> 24:57.758
I HAVE ANOTHER
CAMPAIGN STOP.

24:57.758 --> 24:59.392
OKAY.

24:59.392 --> 25:02.135
WE'RE GOING TO NEW YORK.

25:02.135 --> 25:03.403
OKAY.

25:03.403 --> 25:05.906
IT'S AN IMPORTANT STATE.

25:05.906 --> 25:09.009
GOOD.

25:09.009 --> 25:11.845
I CAN PUSH MY SCHEDULE
A COUPLE HOURS IF...

25:11.845 --> 25:13.647
AND WHY WOULD YOU DO THAT?

25:13.647 --> 25:16.650
TO MAKE SURE YOU'RE OKAY.

25:16.650 --> 25:18.619
WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
I'M NOT OKAY?

25:20.521 --> 25:23.156
YOUR SON.

25:23.156 --> 25:24.257
HE'S DEAD,

25:24.257 --> 25:26.092
AND THERE'S NOTHING
I CAN DO ABOUT IT.

25:28.662 --> 25:30.531
I'M SORRY.

25:30.531 --> 25:31.865
ME, TOO.

25:35.235 --> 25:36.837
LOOK...

25:36.837 --> 25:38.438
I KNOW YOU'RE HURTING.

25:38.438 --> 25:39.973
DO YOU?

25:39.973 --> 25:42.809
YES.

25:42.809 --> 25:45.546
OKAY.

25:45.546 --> 25:48.515
IT HELPS
TO TALK TO SOMEONE.

25:48.515 --> 25:50.383
TALK TO WHO, A DOCTOR?

25:50.383 --> 25:52.185
I DON'T HAVE THAT LUXURY.

25:52.185 --> 25:54.788
YOU CAN TALK TO ME.

25:54.788 --> 25:57.691
ARE YOU A DOCTOR?

25:57.691 --> 25:58.992
NO.

25:58.992 --> 26:00.493
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:00.493 --> 26:05.338
IF I WAS, I'D PROBABLY BE
THE MOST EXPENSIVE ON RECORD.

26:05.338 --> 26:08.642
YOU HAVE THE EAR
OF THE NEXT PRESIDENT.

26:08.642 --> 26:12.045
YOU LOVE THE WAY
THAT SOUNDS.

26:12.045 --> 26:13.647
I LIKE THE WAY YOU SOUND.

26:13.647 --> 26:15.882
♪♪♪♪

26:15.882 --> 26:19.119
LOOK...

26:19.119 --> 26:22.656
I WANT TO TELL YOU SOMETHING,
AND THIS IS IN ALL HONESTY.

26:24.925 --> 26:28.629
WE HAVE VETTED A LOT OF WOMEN
FOR THIS PROCESS.

26:28.629 --> 26:30.496
AND, AS YOU KNOW...

26:30.496 --> 26:32.432
I DON'T LIKE ANY OF THEM.

26:34.200 --> 26:38.304
THEY HAVE THE POLISH,
BUT THEY DON'T HAVE THE EDGE.

26:38.304 --> 26:40.206
THEY DON'T HAVE
THE GUTS..

26:40.206 --> 26:41.241
THE HEART.

26:43.777 --> 26:45.946
THEY DON'T HAVE THE ABILITY
TO HANDLE THE SEAT.

26:48.582 --> 26:51.284
AND THEY CERTAINLY DON'T
MAKE ME FEEL THE WAY YOU DO.

26:55.756 --> 26:57.658
MAYBE...

26:57.658 --> 27:00.026
I WENT ABOUT ALL THIS
THE WRONG WAY.

27:01.868 --> 27:03.103
MAYBE I SHOULD'VE BEEN
HONEST WITH YOU

27:03.103 --> 27:04.505
FROM THE BEGINNING.

27:07.040 --> 27:08.909
YOU WERE.

27:08.909 --> 27:10.777
I WAS?

27:10.777 --> 27:13.079
YEAH.

27:13.079 --> 27:17.250
YOU TOLD ME THE TRUTH.

27:17.250 --> 27:18.685
YOU THINK SO?

27:18.685 --> 27:21.822
YEAH.

27:21.822 --> 27:24.057
A GUY WHO WAS...

27:24.057 --> 27:27.661
POWER TRIPPING AND...

27:27.661 --> 27:29.262
INFO GREEDY,

27:29.262 --> 27:32.065
THAT'S NOT YOU.

27:32.065 --> 27:33.967
THAT'S JUST WHO
YOU WERE TRAINED TO BE.

27:36.369 --> 27:39.372
YOU SEE WHAT I MEAN?

27:39.372 --> 27:41.174
YOU SEE ME.

27:45.111 --> 27:46.513
AND THE SMALLER
THAT BUBBLE GETS,

27:46.513 --> 27:48.214
THE MORE NO ONE SEES ME.

27:50.183 --> 27:52.118
IT'S HARD TO BE THE
MOST‐POWERFUL MAN IN THE WORLD

27:52.118 --> 27:54.521
AND STILL BE INVISIBLE
AT THE SAME TIME.

27:54.521 --> 27:57.891
MM.

27:57.891 --> 28:00.493
SOMETIMES, BEING POWERFUL
MAKES YOU INVISIBLE

28:00.493 --> 28:03.837
TO THOSE WHO WANT
TO LOVE YOU.

28:06.339 --> 28:09.576
I DON'T WANT
TO LEAVE YOU LIKE THIS.

28:09.576 --> 28:11.578
THEN DON'T.

28:11.578 --> 28:14.314
WHAT WOULD YOU
HAVE ME DO?

28:16.249 --> 28:20.253
GIVE IT ALL UP
AND STAY HERE WITH ME.

28:24.725 --> 28:27.160
YOU KNOW
I CAN'T DO THAT.

28:27.160 --> 28:29.129
NOR WOULD YOU.

28:29.129 --> 28:30.664
I WISH I COULD.

28:34.500 --> 28:36.002
YOU CAN ALWAYS COME
VISIT ME.

28:38.672 --> 28:42.075
SHOULD THAT BE BEFORE OR AFTER
I BURY MY SON?

28:42.075 --> 28:43.209
♪♪♪♪

28:43.209 --> 28:44.778
YEAH.

28:44.778 --> 28:46.880
YOU'RE RIGHT.

28:46.880 --> 28:48.414
I'LL LET YOU GRIEVE.

28:50.416 --> 28:51.618
THANK YOU.

29:11.244 --> 29:15.381
♪♪♪♪

29:22.122 --> 29:23.389
[ SIGHS ]

29:35.836 --> 29:38.839
♪♪♪♪

29:49.516 --> 29:50.216
WANT SOMETHING?

29:50.216 --> 29:52.553
NO. I'M OKAY.

29:52.553 --> 29:55.221
HI. HI, BENNY.

29:55.221 --> 29:56.256
HEY, MRS. CRYER.
HOW YOU DOING?

29:56.256 --> 29:58.224
GOOD.
I TRIED TO CALL YOU.

29:58.224 --> 30:00.834
MY PHONE DID RING.

30:00.834 --> 30:02.936
OH.

30:02.936 --> 30:04.037
YOU NEED ANYTHING, MOM?

30:04.037 --> 30:05.806
NO.

30:05.806 --> 30:07.140
ALL RIGHT. I'LL BE BACK
IN A FEW MINUTES.

30:07.140 --> 30:10.010
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

30:10.010 --> 30:13.614
I'M GONNA TALK
TO VERONICA.

30:13.614 --> 30:14.981
OKAY.

30:14.981 --> 30:17.117
I KNOW
YOU DON'T WANT ME TO.

30:17.117 --> 30:20.687
WHATEVER
YOU WANT TO DO.

30:20.687 --> 30:22.455
SHE CAN HELP US,
SO I'M GOING TO CALL HER.

30:22.455 --> 30:24.124
WHATEVER.

30:24.124 --> 30:27.193
BENNY, BEFORE YOU LEAVE,
YOU NEED TO HEAR THIS.

30:27.193 --> 30:29.262
A FUNERAL HOME CALLED,

30:29.262 --> 30:31.732
AND THEY'RE READY.

30:31.732 --> 30:34.400
THEY NEED
SOME CLOTHES FOR HIM.

30:34.400 --> 30:35.736
I DIDN'T WANT
TO TAKE IT UPON MYSELF

30:35.736 --> 30:38.371
TO GATHER HIS THINGS
OR...

30:40.641 --> 30:43.076
I'LL CALL THEM.

30:43.076 --> 30:45.145
WE SHOULD GO BY.

30:45.145 --> 30:46.747
MAMA.
WHAT?

30:46.747 --> 30:48.081
CANDACE NEEDS TO BE
A PART OF THIS.

30:48.081 --> 30:50.951
OH, BENJAMIN.
YOU KNOW I'M RIGHT.

30:53.219 --> 30:54.988
SO, SHE SHOULD BE
A PART OF US BURYING HIM

30:54.988 --> 30:57.190
WHEN SHE WASN'T THERE
WHEN HE WAS ALIVE?

30:57.791 --> 30:59.092
[ SIGHS ]

30:59.092 --> 31:00.627
MOM, I UNDERSTAND
YOU'RE UPSET, OKAY,

31:00.627 --> 31:03.837
BUT I'M RIGHT ABOUT THIS.

31:03.837 --> 31:05.271
YEAH. OKAY.
WHATEVER.

31:05.271 --> 31:07.708
ALL RIGHT.
I'M GONNA GO CALL HER.

31:07.708 --> 31:09.743
WHATEVER.

31:09.743 --> 31:11.111
SHE NOT COMING HERE.

31:11.111 --> 31:12.613
I KNOW, MOM.
SHE NOT COMING HERE.

31:12.613 --> 31:13.980
DON'T WORRY, OKAY.

31:13.980 --> 31:15.516
[ SCOFFS ] THAT GIRL.

31:24.290 --> 31:26.827
IT'S OKAY.

31:28.629 --> 31:30.030
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

31:30.030 --> 31:31.131
[ SIGHS ]

31:31.131 --> 31:33.399
I CAN'T KEEP
STAYING HERE EITHER.

31:33.399 --> 31:35.769
YES. YOU CAN.
NO. I CAN'T.

31:37.938 --> 31:39.840
HANNA, WHEN MY FATHER'S
HOUSE IS THROUGH,

31:39.840 --> 31:42.242
I'M GONNA BE
MOVING IN THERE,

31:42.242 --> 31:44.277
AND I WANT TO GIVE YOU
THIS PLACE.

31:46.580 --> 31:49.683
MRS. CRYER ‐‐
HANNA, I DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT.

31:49.683 --> 31:50.684
♪♪♪♪

31:50.684 --> 31:52.318
YOU CAN'T KEEP
WALKING UP IN MY LIFE

31:52.318 --> 31:53.654
LIKE YOU'RE MY SAVIOR.

31:53.654 --> 31:55.288
I'M NOT TRYING TO
BE YOUR SAVIOR.

31:55.288 --> 31:56.957
WELL, I DON'T WANT
YOUR SYMPATHY EITHER.

31:56.957 --> 32:00.460
AND I'M NOT
GIVING YOU ANY.

32:00.460 --> 32:03.303
THEN WHY YOU TRYING
TO DO THIS?

32:03.303 --> 32:06.206
HANNA,
DON'T TURN THIS AWAY.

32:06.206 --> 32:08.074
I KNOW YOU MAY NOT FEEL
LIKE IT RIGHT NOW,

32:08.074 --> 32:11.745
BUT SOMEBODY UP THERE IS
LOOKING OUT FOR YOU.

32:11.745 --> 32:13.246
KATHERYN.

32:13.246 --> 32:15.315
AND I KNOW YOU'RE PROUD,
AND YOU'VE GOTTEN...

32:15.315 --> 32:18.685
I WANT TO EARN
MY OWN WAY.

32:18.685 --> 32:19.820
OKAY.

32:19.820 --> 32:21.922
THEN COME BACK TO WORK
FOR ME.

32:21.922 --> 32:23.957
I'LL TAKE AHOLD OF THE PLACE
FROM THE BANK,

32:23.957 --> 32:26.627
AND YOU CAN PAY ME EVERY WEEK
JUST LIKE YOU WOULD THEM.

32:26.627 --> 32:28.862
I CAN'T AFFORD THIS.

32:28.862 --> 32:31.231
WELL, I'LL MAKE IT
SO YOU CAN.

32:31.231 --> 32:33.099
NO.

32:33.099 --> 32:35.368
[ SIGHS ]

32:35.368 --> 32:37.070
OKAY,
WE'LL GO TO THE BANK,

32:37.070 --> 32:38.171
AND I'LL MAKE THEM
GIVE YOU A LOAN.

32:38.171 --> 32:40.941
AND YOU CAN PAY THEM.

32:40.941 --> 32:43.043
MY CREDIT.

32:43.043 --> 32:46.179
I'M ON THE BOARD, HANNA.
I CAN MAKE IT HAPPEN.

32:49.149 --> 32:52.418
CAN I THINK ABOUT IT?

32:52.418 --> 32:54.387
YEAH.

32:54.387 --> 32:56.089
YEAH, YOU CAN.

32:58.358 --> 33:00.200
IT DON'T FEEL RIGHT.

33:02.603 --> 33:06.507
HANNA...

33:06.507 --> 33:08.775
WOULD YOU TAKE THIS FROM ME
IF I WAS BLACK?

33:08.775 --> 33:10.611
WHAT DOES THAT
HAVE TO DO WITH IT?

33:10.611 --> 33:13.013
EVERYTHING.

33:13.013 --> 33:14.247
IT HURT ME TO MY SOUL

33:14.247 --> 33:17.784
WHEN YOU SAID
YOU WEREN'T MY SLAVE.

33:17.784 --> 33:19.720
I WAS UPSET.

33:19.720 --> 33:21.988
WELL, NO. I...

33:21.988 --> 33:24.290
GET IT, I GUESS.

33:24.290 --> 33:25.759
YOU THINK THE ONLY WAY
A BLACK MAID

33:25.759 --> 33:27.894
CAN MAKE IT IN THIS WORLD IS
IF A WHITE WOMAN HELPS HER?

33:27.894 --> 33:28.995
NO. I DON'T THINK...

33:28.995 --> 33:32.165
WELL, A LOT
OF SMALL‐MINDED PEOPLE DO.

33:32.165 --> 33:35.501
AND I HOPE
YOU DON'T THINK LIKE THAT.

33:35.501 --> 33:38.038
HANNA...

33:38.038 --> 33:42.509
YOU'VE DONE MORE FOR ME
THAN MY ENTIRE FAMILY.

33:42.509 --> 33:44.477
I WATCHED YOU WASH THE BLOOD
OUT OF MY NIGHTGOWN

33:44.477 --> 33:46.947
WHEN I HAD CANCER.

33:46.947 --> 33:48.348
I SAW YOU PRAYING
FOR MY CHILDREN

33:48.348 --> 33:51.417
WHEN YOU DIDN'T KNOW
I WAS LOOKING.

33:51.417 --> 33:54.588
YOU BROUGHT PEACE INTO MY HOUSE
EVEN IN ALL THAT HELL,

33:54.588 --> 33:57.090
AND YOU DON'T THINK THAT
MEANS ANYTHING TO ME?

34:00.326 --> 34:02.536
I WANT TO GIVE YOU
SOMETHING.

34:05.706 --> 34:08.408
I KNOW TO YOU,
THIS LOOKS LIKE A LOT.

34:08.408 --> 34:11.712
BUT TO ME, IT'S NOTHING.

34:11.712 --> 34:13.680
AND IF I TRIED TO GIVE YOU WHAT
I WANTED TO GIVE YOU,

34:13.680 --> 34:16.249
[CHUCKLES] I KNOW
YOU WOULDN'T TAKE IT.

34:16.249 --> 34:19.820
I KNOW YOU WOULDN'T.

34:19.820 --> 34:22.623
SO LET ME GIVE YOU
THIS LITTLE THING

34:22.623 --> 34:26.727
TO SHOW YOU HOW...
GRATEFUL I AM

34:26.727 --> 34:28.128
♪♪♪♪

34:28.128 --> 34:30.230
AND THAT
I LOVE YOU, HANNA.

34:30.230 --> 34:31.665
I DO.

34:34.367 --> 34:36.302
HANNA, YOU KNOW PEOPLE
WORK ALL THEIR LIVES

34:36.302 --> 34:38.872
AND THEY NEVER SEEM
TO GET AHEAD.

34:38.872 --> 34:40.741
AND THE HARDER THEY WORK,

34:40.741 --> 34:41.875
THEY STAY
RIGHT WHERE THEY ARE.

34:41.875 --> 34:44.911
I'VE SEEN IT FOR YEARS
WITH MY EMPLOYEES.

34:46.980 --> 34:49.816
YOU KNOW...

34:49.816 --> 34:53.219
IT'S OKAY TO LET SOMEONE
GIVE YOU A HAND UP.

34:54.955 --> 34:57.090
IT'S OKAY.

35:03.303 --> 35:05.271
CAN I THINK ABOUT IT?

35:07.774 --> 35:09.109
YES.

35:09.109 --> 35:10.476
IF YOU MUST.

35:13.814 --> 35:18.151
I JUST GOT TO GET
THROUGH THIS FUNERAL.

35:18.151 --> 35:19.520
I UNDERSTAND.

35:23.957 --> 35:25.526
THANK YOU.

35:28.995 --> 35:30.296
THANK YOU.

35:37.197 --> 35:39.005
I KNOW

35:39.005 --> 35:40.373
‐And he did this.
‐CANDACE...

35:40.373 --> 35:41.341
I KNOW.

35:41.341 --> 35:43.376
THAT SON OF A BITCH.

35:43.376 --> 35:44.911
You okay?

35:44.911 --> 35:46.513
[ SIGHS ]
NO, I'M NOT OKAY.

35:46.513 --> 35:47.648
I'M NOT OKAY AT ALL.

35:47.648 --> 35:48.448
ALL RIGHT.
WELL, WHERE YOU AT?

35:48.448 --> 35:50.216
I'LL COME GET YOU.

35:50.216 --> 35:53.319
UH...NO, I'M FINE.

35:53.319 --> 35:54.921
DID YOU HEAR
ANYTHING ABOUT WAR?

35:54.921 --> 35:56.923
HE STILL OUT THERE
LOOKING FOR YOU?

35:56.923 --> 35:59.125
NO. UM...

35:59.125 --> 36:00.527
NO, I'M FINE.

36:00.527 --> 36:03.036
ALL RIGHT. WELL, UH...

36:03.036 --> 36:05.572
WE'RE GONNA HEAD UP
TO THE FUNERAL HOME I THINK.

36:05.572 --> 36:06.740
When?

36:06.740 --> 36:08.108
IN A LITTLE WHILE.

36:08.108 --> 36:10.443
OKAY.

36:10.443 --> 36:11.311
WE'RE GONNA COME GET YOU.

36:11.311 --> 36:13.246
WHO IS WE?

36:13.246 --> 36:15.081
Me and Mama.
BENNY.

36:15.081 --> 36:17.984
COME ON, CANDACE. WHERE YOU AT?
WE'RE GONNA COME GET YOU.

36:17.984 --> 36:21.187
TEXT ME THE ADDRESS.
I'LL ‐‐ I'LL GET THERE.

36:21.187 --> 36:23.957
YOU SURE?
Yeah.

36:23.957 --> 36:25.726
OKAY.
I'M GONNA TEXT YOU NOW.

36:25.726 --> 36:27.561
OKAY. I LOVE YOU.

36:40.941 --> 36:43.844
WHO ARE YOU?

36:43.844 --> 36:46.412
I'M BENNY.
WHO ARE YOU?

36:46.412 --> 36:48.414
I'M JIM CRYER.

36:50.817 --> 36:52.052
KATHERYN HERE
SOMEWHERE?

36:52.052 --> 36:53.887
YEAH,
SHE'S IN THE KITCHEN.

36:53.887 --> 36:56.823
HUH.

36:56.823 --> 36:58.792
HANNA, HI.
HI.

36:58.792 --> 37:00.360
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

37:00.360 --> 37:02.101
WE NEED TO TALK,
KATHERYN.

37:02.101 --> 37:03.570
HOW DID YOU FIND ME?

37:03.570 --> 37:07.574
IT WASN'T THAT DIFFICULT.
YOU'RE NOT THAT HARD TO TRACK.

37:07.574 --> 37:09.342
WELL, YOU CAN GET OUT.

37:09.342 --> 37:10.744
HANNA:
MRS. CRYER, I'MA GO.

37:10.744 --> 37:15.148
NO. HANNA,
YOU'RE NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

37:15.148 --> 37:16.916
I'MA GO ON OVER
TO THE FUNERAL HOME

37:16.916 --> 37:18.752
AND LET Y'ALL TALK.

37:18.752 --> 37:20.153
HANNA.

37:20.153 --> 37:21.822
I'LL BE OVER THERE.

37:23.790 --> 37:25.892
BE RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

37:25.892 --> 37:27.928
BENNY, COME ON.
LET'S GO.

37:34.635 --> 37:36.436
NOW GET THE HELL
OUT OF HERE.

37:36.436 --> 37:37.604
YOU DIDN'T LEAVE ME
MUCH CHOICE.

37:37.604 --> 37:38.772
DID YOU, KATHERYN?

37:38.772 --> 37:40.073
AND WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

37:40.073 --> 37:42.809
IT MEANS YOU BURNED
MY HOUSE DOWN.

37:42.809 --> 37:45.245
YES. YOU'RE LOVELY MANSION
THAT I HATED.

37:45.245 --> 37:46.613
GLAD IT'S GONE.

37:46.613 --> 37:48.849
WHAT THE HELL
HAS GOTTEN INTO YOU?

37:48.849 --> 37:50.450
I DON'T WANT TO BE
THERE ANYMORE, JIM.

37:50.450 --> 37:52.252
WELL, I CAN SEE THAT.

37:52.252 --> 37:56.389
MM, AND I DON'T WANT
TO BE WITH YOU ANYMORE.

37:56.389 --> 37:58.659
WE NEED TO HAVE A MEETING,
ALL OF US.

37:58.659 --> 37:59.893
WHO'S WE?

37:59.893 --> 38:01.367
WE, KATHERYN ‐‐

38:01.367 --> 38:03.837
DAVID, VERONICA,
YOU, ME ‐‐ WE.

38:03.837 --> 38:05.405
I'M NOT DOING
A DAMN THING.

38:05.405 --> 38:06.840
SO YOU WANT TO GO TO JAIL?
IS THAT IT?

38:06.840 --> 38:07.941
IF I HAVE TO.

38:07.941 --> 38:09.543
THAT'S EXACTLY
WHERE YOU'RE GOING,

38:09.543 --> 38:12.879
KATHERYN, UNLESS WE GET
OUR STORIES STRAIGHT.

38:12.879 --> 38:14.280
NO, I AM NOT
TALKING TO YOU.

38:14.280 --> 38:16.517
FINE, THEN SIT YOUR ASS
DOWN ON THE COUCH

38:16.517 --> 38:19.119
AND LISTEN TO ME FOR A CHANGE.

38:19.119 --> 38:21.955
AND I THINK YOU FORGET
WHO THE HELL YOU ARE TALKING TO.

38:21.955 --> 38:23.924
‐YOU ARE NOT HEARING ME.
‐GET OUT OF MY HOUSE.

38:23.924 --> 38:25.425
ON PURPOSE.

38:25.425 --> 38:27.127
IS THAT RIGHT?
YES.

38:27.127 --> 38:32.899
YOU BURNED DOWN
THE HOUSE.

38:32.899 --> 38:34.434
YES.
YEAH.

38:34.434 --> 38:36.169
TO GET RID OF EVIDENCE.

38:36.169 --> 38:40.440
WELL, HERE'S A NEWS FLASH
FOR YOU, KATHERYN CRYER,

38:40.440 --> 38:43.877
YOU PUT THE EVIDENCE
IN STORAGE.

38:43.877 --> 38:45.078
SO...?

38:45.078 --> 38:46.446
SO...?

38:46.446 --> 38:48.014
SO THE RUG,
THE COUCH, THE LAMPS,

38:48.014 --> 38:49.282
EVERYTHING IN THAT HOUSE

38:49.282 --> 38:51.685
THAT YOU PUT
IN STORAGE WAS EVIDENCE.

38:51.685 --> 38:54.688
YOU BURNED DOWN THE HOUSE
FOR NO REASON.

38:54.688 --> 38:56.022
I DON'T CARE

38:58.024 --> 39:00.126
I CAN SEE THAT.

39:00.126 --> 39:02.803
BECAUSE I WAS WISHING
YOU WERE IN IT.

39:04.605 --> 39:05.872
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:10.143 --> 39:11.978
YOU SHOULD BE SO LUCKY.

39:15.549 --> 39:17.050
HANGING AROUND
WITH THAT CRAZY BITCH

39:17.050 --> 39:19.419
HAS GOTTEN YOU EVEN CRAZIER
THAN YOU ALREADY ARE.

39:19.419 --> 39:21.955
NO ONE IS MAKING ME CRAZY
BUT YOU!

39:21.955 --> 39:24.024
CALM DOWN.
I WILL NOT CALM DOWN!

39:24.024 --> 39:25.792
I HAVE TOLD YOU
I WANT A DIVORCE.

39:25.792 --> 39:27.561
I'VE TOLD YOU THAT
I DON'T WANT TO BE WITH YOU.

39:27.561 --> 39:29.596
QUIET.
MOVE!

39:29.596 --> 39:30.964
I LOVE YOU.

39:30.964 --> 39:32.999
[ LAUGHS ]
YOU LOVE ME.

39:32.999 --> 39:34.500
WHAT? DID I SAY
SOMETHING FUNNY?

39:34.500 --> 39:36.269
YES. YOU DON'T LOVE ME.

39:36.269 --> 39:37.671
I DON'T.
YOU LOVE YOUR WHORES.

39:37.671 --> 39:38.839
GO BE WITH THEM.
NO.

39:38.839 --> 39:40.140
I DON'T GET A RAT'S ASS
ABOUT THE WHORES.

39:40.140 --> 39:41.575
‐OH, REALLY?
‐THE DOOR IS THE DOOR IS CLOSED.

39:41.575 --> 39:44.010
SO WHY DID YOU SPEND HALF OF
YOUR LIFE SCREWING THEM, HUH?

39:44.010 --> 39:46.146
YOU DON'T LOVE ME.
YOU LOVE ME.

39:46.146 --> 39:49.382
I LOATHE YOU.

39:49.382 --> 39:52.619
AND I HOPE YOU ROT IN HELL,
YOU SON OF A BITCH.

39:52.619 --> 39:53.654
YOU'RE JUST GONNA THROW IT
ALL AWAY.

39:53.654 --> 39:54.588
I'M NOT GOING TO LEAVE,
ALL RIGHT

39:54.588 --> 39:56.322
BECAUSE I'M STILL
YOUR HUSBAND.

39:56.322 --> 39:58.559
YOU ARE STILL MY WIFE.
ONLY TEMPORARILY.

39:58.559 --> 40:01.094
KATHERYN.

40:01.094 --> 40:03.003
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

40:03.003 --> 40:04.805
YOU DON'T WANT ME.
PUT YOUR CLOTHES ON.

40:04.805 --> 40:06.139
YOU LOVE ME. I DO.

40:06.139 --> 40:08.509
I WANT YOU.

40:08.509 --> 40:10.410
I WANT YOU HERE.

40:10.410 --> 40:11.778
NO.
I WANT YOU NOW.

40:11.778 --> 40:15.015
STOP THIS.
DON'T TOUCH ME.

40:15.015 --> 40:16.216
KATHERYN, YOU LOVE ME.

40:16.216 --> 40:17.784
NO, I DON'T.
YEAH.

40:17.784 --> 40:18.819
I'M NOT HAVING THIS.

40:18.819 --> 40:20.554
IT'S BEEN TOO LONG
TO START OVER.

40:20.554 --> 40:21.855
NO, NO.
STOP IT. STOP IT.

40:21.855 --> 40:23.089
HEY, BABY.
STOP, STOP, STOP.

40:23.089 --> 40:25.759
SO WHAT? WHAT? PLEASE?
[ SOBBING ] NO.

40:25.759 --> 40:27.628
PLEASE!
STOP, PLEASE.

40:27.628 --> 40:28.962
SAY PLEASE.

40:28.962 --> 40:31.898
I WILL NOT.

40:31.898 --> 40:33.867
I AM SO ANGRY AT YOU.
KATHERYN CRYER.

40:33.867 --> 40:38.038
I LOVE YOU, KATHERYN CRYER,
AND YOU LOVE ME.

40:38.038 --> 40:39.706
YES, YOU DO. NO.

40:39.706 --> 40:41.608
[ SOBBING ]
ARE YOU ANGRY?

40:41.608 --> 40:42.809
YES. I'M ANGRY WITH YOU.

40:42.809 --> 40:44.911
OKAY.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

40:44.911 --> 40:46.212
STOP IT.

40:46.212 --> 40:48.181
[ Whispering ]
YOU CAN BE ANGRY.

40:48.181 --> 40:49.449
YOU DESERVE TO BE.

40:51.217 --> 40:52.919
[ WHISPERING
INDISTINCTLY ]

40:54.921 --> 40:56.657
I LIKE IT
WHEN YOU'RE ANGRY.

40:56.657 --> 40:58.158
[ SOBS ]

40:58.158 --> 41:01.367
♪♪♪♪

41:15.048 --> 41:17.283
[ BREATHES HEAVILY ]

41:17.283 --> 41:19.185
IT'S GOOD
TO SEE YOU, KATE.

41:27.460 --> 41:29.696
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:29.696 --> 41:32.566
YOU NEED TO STAY AWAY
FROM HER, JEFFREY.

41:32.566 --> 41:33.734
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

41:33.734 --> 41:35.001
I'M WORKING ON
SOMETHING.

41:35.001 --> 41:37.470
I'M TALKING TO YOU.
CALLING ME FOR MONEY.

41:37.470 --> 41:39.740
TELLING ME YOUR
FAIRY‐TALE DREAMS

41:39.740 --> 41:41.341
AND HOW EXPENSIVE
THINGS WERE.

41:41.341 --> 41:44.878
I WANT YOU TO SLEEP
IN THE BED WITH ME.

41:44.878 --> 41:46.112
YOU DO?
YES.

41:46.112 --> 41:47.380
EVERY NIGHT THAT
YOU'RE HERE.

41:47.380 --> 41:49.850
I WILL TAKE THAT SAME GUN
THAT I BLEW

41:49.850 --> 41:52.152
JENNIFER SALLISON'S BRAINS
OUT WITH,

41:52.152 --> 41:54.688
AND I WILL BLOW YOURS OUT
JUST AS EASY

41:54.688 --> 41:57.490
AS I JUST BLEW YOU.
